40|$|The paper {{deals with}} the Traffic Controllers and ships Pilots {{training}} in marine ports environments. A survey {{of the state of}} the art in this area is presented; in addition two <b>simulators</b> (a <b>ship</b> <b>bridge</b> <b>simulator</b> and a control tower simulator) part of an ongoing research project at University of Calabria are briefly described. The <b>ship</b> <b>bridge</b> <b>simulator</b> and the control tower simulator share the same virtual environment and an initial description of both simulators and their implementation is reported...|$|R
