50|$|The {{vessels are}} to be built by Fincantieri at Riva Trigoso, with {{modifications}} including increased crew capacity of 38. The contract also comprises the provision of logistical support and crew training with each crew completing a 7-week training course. In cooperation with the Marina Militare (Italian Navy), each commissioning crew is provided with a week’s <b>bridge</b> <b>simulator</b> course at the Academy in Livorno.|$|R
